                     <hi rend="largeCaps">JOHN BAILEY</hi> (19)</persName>, was indicted<rs id="t18601126-37-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18601126-37-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18601126-37-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp> for a like offence.</rs>
